<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="4" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="3.[317,1271,852,1795]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">– Variable features: (1) antenna with (19-)20–24(–25) antennomeres; (2) first tergite 1.2 times longer than to as long as broad behind; (3) prosternum + anterior half of pronotum and first tergite testaceous, legs yellow, coxae whitish.</paragraph>
